('Royaume Cyberténébreux', 'Cyberdark Realm', 'spell', 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When this card is activated: You can add 1 \"Cyberdark\" monster from your Deck to your hand, with a different name from the cards in your GY. During your Main Phase, you can: Immediately after this effect resolves, Normal Summon 1 \"Cyberdark\" monster. You can only use the previous effect of \"Cyberdark Realm\" once per turn. If you equip a monster from your GY by the effect of a \"Cyberdark\" monster that activated when it was Normal or Special Summoned, you can equip from your opponent\'s GY instead. You can only activate 1 \"Cyberdark Realm\" per turn.', 'Continuous', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '64753988'),
