('Cybernetic Revolution', 'Cybernetic Revolution', 'trap', 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tribute 1 \"Cyber Dragon\"; Special Summon 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck that lists a \"Cyber Dragon\" monster as material, but it cannot attack directly, and is destroyed during the End Phase of the next turn. You can only activate 1 \"Cybernetic Revolution\" per turn.', 'Normal', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '18597560'),
